<plot>Out of gas and stranded on a deserted road, Billie and her recently widowed elderly mother have no cell phone to call for help. Billie wants to flag down a car, but her mother won't allow it for fear of mass murderers. Confined to the space of the car, they are forced to confront the overwhelming divide that has separated them for years.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?055135</url></doc>
